For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Ekans (TCG Pocket).

Ekans has been featured on 17 different cards since it debuted in the Fossil expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Ekans cards are normally Darkness-type Basic Pokémon.
